1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I take this Silver Key...</font>

2
00:00:03,610 --> 00:00:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You thief.</font>

3
00:00:05,140 --> 00:00:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Racio...</font>

4
00:00:06,550 --> 00:00:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. Your foolishness 
never ceases to amaze me.</font>

5
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So basically, my warnings 
meant nothing to you.</font>

6
00:00:13,780 --> 00:00:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, I know. But...</font>

7
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to do about 
the dual-existence problem?</font>

8
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you go over there, your dual existence 
will become a possibility once again.</font>

9
00:00:27,690 --> 00:00:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! So you were planning to leap 
before you looked, were you?</font>

10
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, if you become its host,</font>

11
00:00:35,300 --> 00:00:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll be trapped once again within 
a time loop you may never escape.</font>

12
00:00:40,550 --> 00:00:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's basically a miracle that you were 
able to end your loop and stand here now.</font>

13
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think you can make 
that miracle happen again?</font>

14
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know... but I'll have time.</font>

15
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time?</font>

16
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

17
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The longer I keep looping, the more time 
I'll have to figure it all out.</font>

18
00:01:04,030 --> 00:01:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

19
00:01:06,250 --> 00:01:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be alone.</font>

20
00:01:07,610 --> 00:01:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I'm looping, 
you'll all still be with me.</font>

21
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll help me reach ideas and decisions 
that I never would have alone...</font>

22
00:01:16,050 --> 00:01:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and most importantly, 
you'll give me courage.</font>

23
00:01:20,130 --> 00:01:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know how much time it'll take.</font>

24
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... If I have all of you, 
I'm certain I'll make it.</font>

25
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To an ending where no one 
has to be unhappy.</font>

26
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've reached a level of foolishness 
where it's actually somehow refreshing.</font>

27
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it, you thief.</font>

28
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is actually the second time 
I've gotten the Silver Key from you.</font>

29
00:01:53,830 --> 00:01:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unbelievable. Then I guess 
you're twice the thief, then.</font>

30
00:02:00,550 --> 00:02:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 20: WORLD OF STARS</font>

31
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A time loop?</font>

32
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're gonna go on a journey 
through time with that thing?</font>

33
00:02:10,250 --> 00:02:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

34
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to fill this Silver Key 
with information once again</font>

35
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and open the dimensional door.</font>

36
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll find Setsu and finally 
connect cause and effect.</font>

37
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:25,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, hearing you talk 
just does my head in, Yuri.</font>

38
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, what do you mean 
by cause and effect?</font>

39
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck's going on?</font>

40
00:02:32,210 --> 00:02:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears that an 
explanation is in order.</font>

41
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are the narrator, are you not?</font>

42
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain so everyone can understand.</font>

43
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

44
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of you have any memories 
of my past loops or of Setsu.</font>

45
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

46
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Setsu that was in this world</font>

47
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">used my filled Silver Key 
to open a dimensional door,</font>

48
00:02:59,290 --> 00:03:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">crossing over to another dimension 
with its own, separate cause and effect.</font>

49
00:03:03,650 --> 00:03:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But their own Silver Key still isn't full,
which means they can't escape the loop.</font>

50
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm going to fill 
this Silver Key once more,</font>

51
00:03:14,090 --> 00:03:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">open the door, and go 
over to the other side.</font>

52
00:03:17,140 --> 00:03:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that Setsu can close their loop.</font>

53
00:03:21,060 --> 00:03:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will going over there be enough 
for you to close Setsu's loop, Yuri?</font>

54
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should, if they give me 
their Silver Key.</font>

55
00:03:29,690 --> 00:03:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But filling up a Silver Key 
is really difficult, isn't it?</font>

56
00:03:36,610 --> 00:03:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you'll be able 
to find them again?</font>

57
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no idea.</font>

58
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have to try.</font>

59
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing ventured, 
nothing gained, I suppose...</font>

60
00:03:45,410 --> 00:03:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You keep spoutin' off all these excuses,</font>

61
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you're just chasin' after some chick 
you have the hots for, aren't ya?</font>

62
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! For real?!</font>

63
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, Setsu's non-binary, though.</font>

64
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they get you excited, 
don't they? I sorta get it.</font>

65
00:04:01,810 --> 00:04:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I have a feeling you'd like them.</font>

66
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds A-okay to me!</font>

67
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cheater!</font>

68
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

69
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you strung 
cute li'l SQ along all this time.</font>

70
00:04:13,890 --> 00:04:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ch-Cheater?</font>

71
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better take responsibility for this!</font>

72
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For that night when we totes 
shared a bed during warp!</font>

73
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri... How could you?</font>

74
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yuri, you... You're just a...</font>

75
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait! That's not true!</font>

76
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. Knock it off with the jokes.</font>

77
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not a joke.</font>

78
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always thought... cute li'l SQ was 
actually someone special to you.</font>

79
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least, that's what your eyes said!</font>

80
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">SQ...</font>

81
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're very precious to me.</font>

82
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and everyone here.</font>

83
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the reason I'm even able to be here 
right now is because of Setsu.</font>

84
00:04:58,140 --> 00:05:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I can't bear the thought 
of them suffering all alone.</font>

85
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

86
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just can't let that happen.</font>

87
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... We should probably do a toast?</font>

88
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Let's send them off with a bang!</font>

89
00:05:15,410 --> 00:05:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have fun preparin' and stuff. 
I'mma go back to my room.</font>

90
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

91
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemme go!</font>

92
00:05:22,210 --> 00:05:26,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will start the preparations. 
Jina, will you assist me?</font>

93
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

94
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

95
00:05:34,610 --> 00:05:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

96
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your forehead's gotta 
be glued to the ground!</font>

97
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this!</font>

98
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

99
00:05:47,450 --> 00:05:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heck are they doing?</font>

100
00:05:48,770 --> 00:05:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri wanted to learn how to grovel.</font>

101
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's, uh... different.</font>

102
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were saying it'd be 
an essential skill for their future.</font>

103
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that hurt, damn it!</font>

104
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this was your idea, Shigemichi.</font>

105
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said, "I'll show you just 
how tough my skin is!"</font>

106
00:06:12,570 --> 00:06:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, well...</font>

107
00:06:15,590 --> 00:06:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuriko...</font>

108
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that getup?</font>

109
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this not a costume party?</font>

110
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cute, Yurikocchi!</font>

111
00:06:27,450 --> 00:06:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You piece of trash. You deceived me.</font>

112
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tee-hee!</font>

113
00:06:32,010 --> 00:06:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What chaos.</font>

114
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I suppose observing from the eye of 
the storm is also a form of entertainment.</font>

115
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here are some snacks Jina prepared.</font>

116
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disgusting.</font>

117
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's brutally honest.</font>

118
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Gnosia incident that 
took place on Planet Liu-An...</i></font>

119
00:06:55,670 --> 00:07:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the fifteen that just happened 
to take refuge from it on this ship...</i></font>

120
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is one heckuva party!</font>

121
00:07:02,970 --> 00:07:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's having fun!</font>

122
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've started to think that it wasn't just 
coincidence that brought us together.</i></font>

123
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For myself, for everyone here... No,</i></font>

124
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this was a vital part of 
the whole world's destiny.</i></font>

125
00:07:20,410 --> 00:07:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It couldn't have happened any other way.</i></font>

126
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And each and every one of them 
was an irreplaceable part of it.</i></font>

127
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're all my precious friends.</i></font>

128
00:07:35,290 --> 00:07:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, I'm at a 
complete loss for words.</font>

129
00:07:40,530 --> 00:07:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Racio?</font>

130
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess staying in my room 
was the right choice.</font>

131
00:07:50,710 --> 00:07:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

132
00:07:52,470 --> 00:07:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was bored, so I compiled it all.</font>

133
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything that'll happen henceforth, 
and everything you'll need to do.</font>

134
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, you truly are a fool.</font>

135
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I honestly can't see this ending well.</font>

136
00:08:09,860 --> 00:08:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

137
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I start looping again, 
these things will happen...</font>

138
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is amazing! You're amazing, Racio!</font>

139
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll explain everything you need to know, 
so drill it into that brain of yours.</font>

140
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that's the only thing you 
can take with you on these loops.</font>

141
00:08:28,550 --> 00:08:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right...</font>

142
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're exactly right.</font>

143
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there you have it.</font>

144
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! That's a perfect plan!</font>

145
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In what way? My reasoning itself 
was perfect, I'll give you that,</font>

146
00:08:43,830 --> 00:08:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but in practice, I'd say it's nearly 
impossible for you to pull off.</font>

147
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:51,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true. But I'll do my best.</font>

148
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't let your efforts go to waste.</i></font>

149
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, I just don't understand you.</font>

150
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To go to so much trouble 
and put yourself in so much danger</font>

151
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all for another's sake... It's beyond me.</font>

152
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure about that?</font>

153
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you trying to say?</font>

154
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just so you know, 
I didn't do this for you.</font>

155
00:09:19,090 --> 00:09:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

156
00:09:21,450 --> 00:09:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I first awakened here, 
I felt nothing but despair.</font>

157
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no memories, 
there was a Gnosia on board,</font>

158
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and everyone was suspicious of each other.</font>

159
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you were the coldest 
out of everyone, Racio.</font>

160
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You constantly treated me like a Gnosia 
and tried to send me into cold sleep.</font>

161
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, I couldn't help 
but think time and time again,</font>

162
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"If only they weren't here."</font>

163
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'd like to tell my past 
self that they were wrong.</font>

164
00:09:57,510 --> 00:10:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That the unfriendly, sharp-tongued 
individual standing before them</font>

165
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a genuinely kind person, 
not that they'll ever show it,</font>

166
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and will help them when no one else can.</font>

167
00:10:10,090 --> 00:10:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph. Don't get the wrong idea.</font>

168
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just came to laugh at the 
poor, pathetic guinea pig</font>

169
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the Silver Key 
is about to make its new host.</font>

170
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

171
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yurinchy...</font>

172
00:10:32,290 --> 00:10:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

173
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

174
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

175
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

176
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

177
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:48,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jina...</font>

178
00:10:48,970 --> 00:10:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like... I've said goodbye 
to you many times before, Yuri.</font>

179
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same here.</font>

180
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

181
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

182
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no further hesitations or regrets.</i></font>

183
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to reach Setsu...</i></font>

184
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and bring about a conclusion 
where all our loops can end.</i></font>

185
00:11:22,370 --> 00:11:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doubt not. Fear not. And know.</font>

186
00:11:26,290 --> 00:11:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowledge will save all.</font>

187
00:12:54,560 --> 00:13:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's begin. This discussion will 
determine whether we survive.</font>

188
00:13:06,930 --> 00:13:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder how much time 
has passed since then.</i></font>

189
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I continue looping over and over,</i></font>

190
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've noticed a lot of things 
that are different from before.</i></font>

191
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

192
00:13:20,770 --> 00:13:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awake. Are you feeling okay?</font>

193
00:13:24,850 --> 00:13:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

194
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>First, no matter how many loops I do, 
Setsu isn't present in any of them.</i></font>

195
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I expected as much.</i></font>

196
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After all, when Setsu went 
through the dimensional door,</i></font>

197
00:13:38,610 --> 00:13:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they ceased to exist in this universe.</i></font>

198
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But also...</i></font>

199
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:48,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Comet... Is there anyone named 
Kukrushka on board this ship?</font>

200
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukrushka?</font>

201
00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't ring a bell.</font>

202
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

203
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Along with Setsu, Kukrushka 
also seems to have disappeared.</i></font>

204
00:14:00,330 --> 00:14:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She won't show up regardless 
of how many loops I do, either.</i></font>

205
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, technically, she hasn't 
disappeared completely.</i></font>

206
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's asleep in storage as a doll.</i></font>

207
00:14:13,010 --> 00:14:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she hasn't once awoken or moved,</i></font>

208
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and she hasn't gone 
on any killing sprees, either.</i></font>

209
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on? Could this have been 
caused in some way by Setsu's absence?</i></font>

210
00:14:29,010 --> 00:14:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri.</font>

211
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

212
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us begin the meeting posthaste.</font>

213
00:14:34,890 --> 00:14:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Of course.</font>

214
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not good. I can't let myself 
get distracted now.</i></font>

215
00:14:42,130 --> 00:14:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to do everything I can to fill the 
Silver Key so I can see Setsu again.</i></font>

216
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">LeVi, can I get a count 
of the Gnosia on board?</font>

217
00:14:50,570 --> 00:14:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Certainly. I am detecting two Gnosia.</i></font>

218
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so, my looping continues anew.</i></font>

219
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:22,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've eliminated all of the Gnosia, 
and both you and I have survived.</font>

220
00:15:22,690 --> 00:15:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said that if I fulfilled both those 
conditions, you'd tell me the truth.</font>

221
00:15:27,310 --> 00:15:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think you'd actually win.</font>

222
00:15:30,590 --> 00:15:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem quite intelligent 
for a bit player.</font>

223
00:15:34,170 --> 00:15:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I have looped through 
all this many, many times...</font>

224
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in order to reach this world line.</font>

225
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Silver Key...</font>

226
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. And that's why I know...</font>

227
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">exactly what you're about to tell me.</font>

228
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oho. What an interesting thing to say.</font>

229
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, do enlighten me.</font>

230
00:15:57,530 --> 00:15:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to tell me what I really am.</font>

231
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a Bug—</font>

232
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">something created by Gnos that 
shouldn't exist in this world at all.</font>

233
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Apparently I was wrong 
to call you a bit player.</font>

234
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you knew all that already, why did 
you persist in winning this game?</font>

235
00:16:22,210 --> 00:16:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a request.</font>

236
00:16:27,940 --> 00:16:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Hoshibune?</font>

237
00:16:29,830 --> 00:16:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. If we can get within 
communication range,</font>

238
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it should be possible 
to hack into their system.</font>

239
00:16:36,380 --> 00:16:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a foolish plan. 
If you fail, we won't get off lightly.</font>

240
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no...</font>

241
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, 
you can blame it all on me.</font>

242
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can just say I hijacked the ship.</font>

243
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And my compensation?</font>

244
00:16:52,990 --> 00:16:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Jonas, am not so charitable 
as to work without recompense.</font>

245
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has you there.</font>

246
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, I don't have money 
or any other form of payment.</font>

247
00:17:09,890 --> 00:17:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph.</font>

248
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

249
00:17:14,300 --> 00:17:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, you and your ship will have 
another heroic tale to add to your legend.</font>

250
00:17:18,770 --> 00:17:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tell of how you confronted the 
Hoshibune, infamous for cyberization,</font>

251
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when even the military 
held back on facing them.</font>

252
00:17:27,730 --> 00:17:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll go down in history.</font>

253
00:17:31,890 --> 00:17:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stella.</font>

254
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

255
00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set a course for the Hoshibune.</font>

256
00:17:40,530 --> 00:17:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He may seem like a jaded, 
cold-hearted adult,</i></font>

257
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but deep inside, he still loves 
adventure and competition.</i></font>

258
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've watched him long enough to know...</i></font>

259
00:17:48,870 --> 00:17:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that Jonas is still a boy at heart.</i></font>

260
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get there safe and sound.</font>

261
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the route to the 
Hoshibune is unknown.</font>

262
00:18:00,540 --> 00:18:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please guide us.</font>

263
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you to command me?</font>

264
00:18:05,380 --> 00:18:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I suppose this will make 
for an adequate diversion.</font>

265
00:18:32,340 --> 00:18:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the Hoshibune.</font>

266
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyberization?</font>

267
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

268
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The key to solving the dual-existence 
problem likely lies within cyberization.</font>

269
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can travel between dimensions 
by cyberizing your consciousness...</font>

270
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the whole dual-existence 
thing won't happen!</font>

271
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct.</font>

272
00:18:53,410 --> 00:18:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that means you'll have to find 
and make use of <i>them</i>.</font>

273
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you certain about this?</font>

274
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you succeed in 
cyberizing your consciousness,</font>

275
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's a possibility that Gnos 
will instantly swallow you up.</font>

276
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, there's nothing I can do.</font>

277
00:19:12,650 --> 00:19:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I want to believe 
that Gnos won't do that.</font>

278
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send a call sign to the Hoshibune.</font>

279
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send the call sign.</font>

280
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you wish.</font>

281
00:19:28,260 --> 00:19:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go to the pod that we prepared.</font>

282
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

283
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please... let this go as planned.</i></font>

284
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Gnos swallows me up, it's all over.</i></font>

285
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And not even Yuriko or Racio 
knows if that will happen.</i></font>

286
00:19:52,990 --> 00:19:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I can do is pray.</i></font>

287
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

288
00:20:05,170 --> 00:20:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please... Please... Please... Please...</i></font>

289
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sha-ming.</i></font>

290
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Remnan.</i></font>

291
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Otome.</i></font>

292
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kukrushka.</i></font>

293
00:20:21,410 --> 00:20:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Jonas.</i></font>

294
00:20:23,130 --> 00:20:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Chipie.</i></font>

295
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Comet.</i></font>

296
00:20:26,390 --> 00:20:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuriko.</i></font>

297
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stella.</i></font>

298
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shigemichi.</i></font>

299
00:20:31,370 --> 00:20:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Jina.</i></font>

300
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Racio.</i></font>

301
00:20:34,530 --> 00:20:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>SQ.</i></font>

302
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Setsu!</i></font>

303
00:20:59,140 --> 00:21:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gnos...?</font>

304
00:21:12,260 --> 00:21:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's full.</font>

305
00:21:30,430 --> 00:21:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I know.</font>

306
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

307
00:22:27,210 --> 00:22:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand?</font>

